
# Quick Start

> **Need full setup?** See [ONBOARDING.md](ONBOARDING.md) for tool installation
> or [SETUP.md](SETUP.md) for project configuration.

## Prerequisites

- Python {{ python_version }}+
- [UV](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/) package manager
- [go-task](https://taskfile.dev/) task runner
- [Bun](https://bun.sh/) for frontend
- {{ container_runtime }} for containers

## Clone and Run

```bash
git clone <repository-url>
cd {{ project_slug }}

# Full setup (deps + pre-commit + .env)
task setup

# Start development servers
task dev
```

## Common Commands

```bash
task backend:test

task backend:lint

task backend:format

task backend:typecheck

task frontend:dev

task docker:up

task docker:logs
```

